title: Amazing sunsets, privacy, spacious 4 bed/3.5 bath/2 c gar HOUSE!
map_address: Pegan Lane (Private Lane) near Pleasant Street South
broker_fee: One month rent as fee to LA
posting_body: ['Extraordinary large house offered for rent!', 'Fabulous sunset vistas!', 'Vacation at home!', 'Work from home!', 'Renovated and updated Contemporary Gabriel Colonial is located in a tranquil setting abutting Belkin Lookout Farm and multi million $ neighborhood on South Natick/Dover line.', 'Offers open and flexible floor plan, great for entertaining and easy everyday living.', 'Sprawling 1st floor offers: open eat-in kitchen with cherry cabinets and center island with Corian countertop, located next to a family room with wood stove and built-in bookcases.', 'Mudroom has plenty of storage closets, and access to large 2 car garage with storage shelving, half bath with laundry.', 'There is office/dinning room and large living room with a fireplace.', 'Sunken Great Room opens with glass doors to a massive deck, French doors open to an office suite/library with a separate exterior entrance.', 'Flexible floor plan offers opportunity to create two separate home offices on 1st floor with hardwired Internet connections.', 'Second floor offers luxurious main suite with en-suite bath: marble shower with multiple heads, Jacuzzi tub, double vanity and walk-in closet.', 'Opposite 2nd floor wing offers three additional bedrooms, with one of them is with en-suite full bath, and additional full bathroom off the hallway.', 'Hardwood floors throughout.', 'Central a/c. Beautiful yard w/fruit trees, patio under a pergola w/grape wines.', "House is located in a country setting but in a commuter's location, just minutes to Natick Center, near Wellesley Collage and Wellesley Center and with two commuter train stations to Boston.", 'Available for September 1st move in date.', 'Pets accepted.', 'Tenant to bring their own washer and dryer.', 'Professionally managed.', 'Available for long term lease.', 'Tenant pays own utilities: water & sewer (Town of Natick), heating oil, electricity, cable/Internet.', 'Tenant takes care of lawn moving, yard maintenance, snow plowing.', 'Trash removal provided by curbside trash & recyclables pick up by Town of Natick municipal services.', 'Tenant pays one month fee to the Listing Agency.', 'Landlord requires 1st month and one month security.', 'Please call Marta (781-694-4049) leave a message, or email.', 'Please do not text.']
